<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580749190.jpg" alt="1773580749190.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580749190.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580606328.jpg" alt="1773580606328.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580606328.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580621616.jpg" alt="1773580621616.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580621616.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580634675.jpg" alt="1773580634675.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580634675.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580666097.jpg" alt="1773580666097.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580666097.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580678079.jpg" alt="1773580678079.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580678079.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580688613.jpg" alt="1773580688613.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580688613.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580698535.jpg" alt="1773580698535.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580698535.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580708491.jpg" alt="1773580708491.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1773580708491.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>春之韵</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">江软春风揽芳洲，先锋小镇郁金稠。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">千畦叠彩凝霞色，一路飘香入眼眸。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">翠叶摇风承晓露，繁英弄影醉春游。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">校园胜景藏诗意，不负韶光踏锦流。</span></p>